A Brand Proven to Build Business
The Allstate name gives your business instant credibility in helping attract new customers and establishing you in the community. Whether you start your own agency or buy an existing one, you’ll have a Fortune 100 company with over 85 years of innovation and leadership behind you.


 
Build New


 
Buy Existing



Build New
Starting an agency from scratch lets you lay out your own vision and bring it to life the way you want. You’ll hire your own staff, build a customer base and even create your own marketing plan. 
“I was able to build a successful business the way I wanted” —Alyson Sabatini, Allstate Agency Owner
Allstate offers ongoing education and support on products, sales techniques, productivity tips and marketing tools. You’ll also have a local, dedicated Field Sales Leader who will provide one-on-one support to you and your agency.


Buy Existing
Going this route gives you a fast start in growing with an established customer base and no limits on what you can earn.
“I had a solid base that allowed me to take my agency to the next level” —David Gonzalez, Allstate Agency Owner
Even though you’re buying an existing agency, you can still run your business the way you want. Plus, you’ll get ongoing education and support on products, sales techniques, productivity tips and marketing tools. And if you have questions along the way, a local Field Sales Leader is just a phone call away.


Start Your Search
Learn even more at Allstateagent.com >



