Best Insurance Companies
Below is a list of the best insurance companies and brokers that we recommend. Every company has been screened and selected based on specific criteria for each insurance type.
Auto Home Life Medicare Health Travel Business
Auto Insurance


Get a Quote

Why: Progressive is a top insurer for cars in the United States and consistently ranks high in customer satisfaction. Since they cut out the middlemen and sell directly to customers, Progressive is able to keep their rates very low. Individuals can get an auto insurance quote directly from their website or over the phone. Progressive can also provide insurance for homeowners, renters and motorcycle owners, and is a great choice for anyone with a need for multiple lines of coverage.


Home Insurance


Get a Quote

Why: Progressive pioneered the buying process of car insurance online, and have used the same technology to provide affordable home insurance coverage across the country. Progressive is consistently one of the highest-rated in customer satisfaction when it comes to their policyholders. With 24/7 claims filing online and over the phone, you can rest assured that one of your biggest assets is protected.


Life Insurance


Get a Quote

Speak with a Life Insurance Specialist
(844) 611-3271
Why: Globe Life is one of the leading term life insurance companies in the US. They offer policies to individuals without a medical exam, and they make the entire life insurance buying process quick and easy. With coverage in nearly every state and a long history within the industry, Globe Life is a leader at providing coverage from coast to coast. Anyone looking for life insurance coverage should start with them.


Medicare Supplement Insurance


Get a Quote

Speak with a Medicare Supplement Insurance Specialist
(844) 611-2338
Why: Expert Insurance Reviews works hand-in-hand with one of the industry’s leading providers of Medicare supplement quotes. They connect thousands of individuals every month with top Medicare supplement insurance companies. The process starts with a simple zip code form, and allows individuals to view multiple companies that provide services in their area. The cost is the same as going directly to the insurance company, but offers a clearer picture of what is available.


Health Insurance


Get a Quote

Speak with a Health Insurance Specialist
(844) 334-6350
Why: HealthSherpa is a full service broker that provides numerous options for individuals and families looking to purchase health insurance. Their website is easy to use, and the policy premiums are the same price as purchasing directly from an insurance carrier. We recommend using a broker when shopping for health insurance because it makes the process much easier when comparing features and prices between the available plans.


Travel Insurance


Get a Quote

Why: Travelex offers a number of comprehensive travel insurance products that can accommodate a range of travelers. Whether you are looking for protection while you are on a quick solo trip abroad, or will be traveling with your entire family for an extended period of time, Travelex has a policy right for you.
Business Insurance


Get a Quote

Why: Hiscox Insurance can provide businesses with all their insurance needs. They offer General Liability, Business Property, Workers Compensation, Commercial Auto, Business Umbrella and Errors & Omissions. Their quoting process is quick and straightforward, and they are a top provider of business insurance in the United States.
 


